# Files Wrangler must NOT upload as static assets (the deploy scans the repo root).
# The deployed site is just index.html + /engines + _headers. Everything else here is
# either build-time (node_modules — incl. the 119 MiB workerd binary), dev source, or
# repo metadata, and must be excluded or it trips the 25 MiB per-asset limit.

node_modules
.git
.github
.wrangler
src
test
build
plan
*.log
*.md
.gitignore
.assetsignore
wrangler.jsonc
package.json
package-lock.json
bun.lockb
VERSION
